frames.caption: A woman rests peacefully on a rock by the sea, with her eyes closed as the golden sunset bathes the scene in warm light. Her wet hair cascades down, blending with the shimmering water around her.
frames.description: The scene captures a tranquil moment at the seaside during sunset. The woman appears relaxed and serene, with the ocean waves gently lapping against the rocks.

frames.caption: A young woman with wet hair is lying on a rock by the sea, smiling gently as the sun sets in the background. The golden light of the sunset reflects off the water, creating a warm and serene atmosphere. Her relaxed posture and content expression suggest a moment of peaceful enjoyment.
frames.description: The scene captures a tranquil moment at the seaside during sunset. The woman appears to be enjoying the natural beauty around her, with the ocean waves gently lapping against the rocks.
